<Content>Good value This hotel appears to have undergone a recent renovation. The rooms were fresh and clean and the beds were comfortable. There is a plasma television, free wifi internet, a security safe, and a nice, clean bathroom. The climate controls worked perfectly and the hotel was quiet. I especially like the location, one block from the Paseo de la Reforma, and the proximity of many good eateries. I had some great enchiladas de mole on Rio Lerma just across Rio Mississippi. I will stay here again!-dgh 
