<Content>Casa Inn The Casa Inn is fabulous - great location at a reasonable rate (walking distance to Zona Rosa and the angel statue). Breakfast and lunch buffets are great - very friendly and attentive staff. Internet in the downstairs lobby. Rooms are standard size and the bathroom/shower are very spacious. The check-in desk can be a little intimidating b/c not everyone speaks English, but in general they are pretty patient with travelers. I would definitely recommend the Inn. 
